Description: Hello,
We have recently migrated our on-prem user home directories to OneDrive and I need to create permissions reports for our users. Unfortunately, I am not seeing all subdirectories. I currently see Social, Documents, Form Template and Style Library. How can I see all subdirectories in and their permissions if shared with other users?

Next Steps Updated: Setting up meeting to look at the needed Access

Netwrix Enterprise Auditor v11.6 > Requirements > SharePoint Solution > SharePoint Scan Options > SharePoint Online Permissions
https://helpcenter.netwrix.com/bundle/EnterpriseAuditor_11.6/page/Content/EnterpriseAuditor/Requirements/Solutions/SharePoint/OnlinePermissions.htm

What We've Learned Updated: The remote server returned an ERROR: (401) Unauthorized.
